wdi2-NY.EXP.CAPM.KN.def: Exports as a capacity to import equals the current price value of exports of goods and services deflated by the import price index. Data are in constant local currency.
wdi2-NY.EXP.CAPM.KN.name: Exports as a capacity to import
wdi2-NY.EXP.CAPM.KN.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
